} goNext() { const { swiper } = this.state; if (swiper !== null) { swiper.slideNext(); } } goPrev() { const { swiper } = this.state; if (swiper !== null) { swiper.slidePrev(); } } handleScroll() { if (window.scrollY > 70) { this.setState({ scrollBtn: true });
